Guguwar Rosa ta yi barazanar Phoenix, Las Vegas da Salt Lake City da ambaliyar ruwa (yana iya zama da amfani ga yankunan bushe)
Ba kasafai ake samun matsin lamba mai zafi a Arizona ba, amma mai yiwuwa hakan zai faru ne a farkon mako mai zuwa lokacin da sauran ƙarfin guguwar Rosa ke wucewa ta yankin hamadar kudu maso yamma, yana haifar da haɗarin ambaliyar ruwa.
Hukumar kula da yanayi ta jihar ta riga ta ba da gargadin yiwuwar ambaliyar ruwa a ranar Litinin da Talata a yammacin Arizona, har zuwa kudancin Nevada da gabashin Nevada, kudu maso gabashin California da Utah, ciki har da Phoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas da Sweet Lake City.
Ana sa ran Rosa za ta bi hanyar kai tsaye ta Phoenix a ranar Talata, ta yi nisa da yamma a ranar Litinin.
