"Na fito ne domin 'ya'yana, wurinmu a Turai ne", in ji Joshe Tanevski, mai shekara 62, mai jefa kuri'a a babban birnin kasar, Skopje.
Firayim Ministan Macedonia Zoran Zaev, matarsa Zorica da dan su Dusko sun kada kuri'arsu a zaben raba gardama a Macedonia kan sauya sunan kasar, wanda zai share fagen shiga kungiyar NATO da kungiyar tarayyar Turai, a ranar 30 ga Satumba, 2018 a Strumica.
