Tashar YouTube ta taron Trump a West Virginia
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara gangamin gangamin yakin neman zabe a garin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, ciki har da ziyarar wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da kuri'un tabbatar da zabensa don cike gurbin da ke gaban kotun kolin ke cikin nutsuwa, Trump na kokarin gina goyon baya ga zaben da ke tafe a tsakiyar wa'adinsa, saboda 'yan Republican na iya rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a zaben na watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump na yammacin Virginia zai kasance kuma ta yaya za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a karfe 7 na yammacin yammacin yammacin yammacin yammacin ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia ta hanyar Intanet tare da watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
A wannan makon ne dai Trump zai yi jawabi a gaban wanda ya tsayar da shi a kotun kolin kasar, Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ya samu karbuwa sakamakon zargin cin zarafin da ake yi masa na lalata da ake sa ran zai jinkirta kada kuri'ar majalisar dattijai har na mako guda, yayin da hukumar FBI ke gudanar da bincike.
Babban manufar taron shi ne taimakawa 'yan Republican su samu ci gaba a zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A cewar kamfanin yakin neman zaben shugaba Trump, taron gangamin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafa gwiwa tsakanin masu ba da agaji da magoya baya" yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma fadada rinjaye a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai, a cewar Reuters.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci a cikin ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin yakin neman zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump ga Reuters, wanda ya ki amincewa da a ambaci sunansa.
An shirya taron ne a gidan wasan kwaikwayo na West Bank a Wheeling, taron na yau da dare zai iya jawo magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma kafofin watsa labarai daga Pittsburgh, a cewar West Virginia Metro News.
A ranar Asabar ne ziyarar Trump ta biyu zuwa West Virginia a cikin wata daya, jihar da ya lashe da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican daga West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ke kan gaba a zaben.
"Ba shi da kyau ga Morrissey cewa shugaban ya zo don inganta shahararrun kuri'un", in ji Simon Heather, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar Reuters.
