Tun da yawancin 'yan Republican ba su kula da ko kare takarar Brett Kavanaugh a Kotun Koli ba duk da zargin da ake yi na cin zarafin jima'i, manazarta sun yi gargadin cewa za a sami mummunan sakamako, musamman daga mata a cikin zaben tsakiyar zangon.
