Ya so ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne", in ji shi, don kada ya sa kowa ya yi takaici idan suka san cewa shi ɗan luwaɗi ne.
Wannan ɗan wasan Olympics mai zinare biyu ya zama sanannen mai tallafawa kamfen ɗin LGBT kuma ya yi amfani da wasan kwaikwayonsa a wasannin Commonwealth na wannan shekara a Ostiraliya don yin kira ga ƙasashe da yawa da su haramta luwadi.
Ya ce ya yi magana a fili domin yana farin cikin kasancewa a buɗe ba tare da rarrabuwa ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu bege.
Gwarzon zakaran duniya sau uku ya ce ya yi soyayya da wani mutum - wani dan fim din Amurka mai suna Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013 - "Ya ba ni mamaki".
Daley ta auri Oscar, wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, a shekarar da ta gabata, amma ta ce bambancin shekaru bai taɓa zama matsala ba.
"Idan ka sha wahala sosai tun kana ƙarami" - ya halarci gasar Olympics na farko yana ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon kansa shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce yana da wuya a sami wani a shekarunsa da ya taɓa fuskantar irin wannan tsayi da zurfin.
Sun haifi ɗa a watan Yuni mai suna Robert Ray Black-Dale, kuma Daly ya ce duk yadda yake kallon sa ya canza.
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, duk abin da ya shafi shi ne, 'Ina bukatar lashe lambar zinare,'" in ji shi.
