Girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a ƙasar Indonesia
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a wata girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta afkawa birnin Palo na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a, in ji jami'ai, kuma ana sa ran adadin wadanda suka mutu zai karu.
Sakamakon katsewar sadarwa, masu ba da agaji ba za su iya samun bayanai daga gundumar Donggala ba, wani yanki da ke arewacin Palo wanda ya fi kusa da cibiyar girgizar kasar mai karfin awo 7.5.
Bayan wannan bala'in, an kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga Palo.
Ga wasu muhimman bayanai game da Palo da Dongola, a tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palo shine babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, wanda ke kan iyakar wani ɗan gajeren bakin teku a gabar yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Dongola wani yanki ne da ke da nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar teku a arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
Gundumar, wacce ke wakiltar yanki ne na gudanarwa a cikin lardin, a cikin 2017 tana da ƙididdigar yawan jama'a 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune manyan hanyoyin samun kudin shiga ga tattalin arzikin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi, musamman a yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na Nickel yana da muhimmiyar aiki a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morawai, a gefen tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i a ƙasar Indonesia ta ce an yi wa garin Palo da Donggala tsunami sau da yawa a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗaruruwan gidaje a Donggala.
Tsunami kuma ya afkawa yammacin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Pacific kuma tana fuskantar girgizar ƙasa a kai a kai.
Wasu daga cikin manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami a cikin 'yan shekarun nan sune:
2004: Girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske a gabar yammacin lardin Aceh na Indonesia a arewacin Sumatra a ranar 26 ga Disamba ta haifar da tsunami wanda ya afku a kasashe 14, inda ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su mazauna Aceh.
2005: Ƙarƙashin teku mai ƙarfi ya afku a yammacin Sumatra a ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias, a bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, ta jawo tsunami da ya lalata gabar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 ta afku a yankin da ke kusa da garin Padang, babban birnin lardin West Sumatra.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 sun mutu.
2010: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta afkawa tsibirin Mentawai, kusa da Sumatra, ta haifar da tsunami mai zurfin mita 10, ta lalata ƙauyuka da yawa, kuma ta kashe mutane 300.
2016: Wata girgizar kasa mai zurfi ta afku a gundumar Pidi Jaya da ke Aceh, inda ta haifar da bala'i da firgici kamar yadda ta tunatar da mutane game da mummunar girgizar kasa da tsunami a shekarar 2004.
A wannan lokacin, girgizar ba ta haifar da tsunami ba, amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu saboda gine-ginen da suka rushe.
